snippet.title: Box Party Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
You're invited to the biggest party of the year!
But the food has gone bad, and they're threatening to crash the party, forever!
It's up to you to stop them before it's too late!

Box Party Demo will release sometime in December 2021.

-Box Party on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1727350/Box_Party/
-Box Party on itch.io:
https://idiotbitz.itch.io/box-party
